'''劉永'''（{{lang-en|Antony Lau}}，{{bd|1952年|2月7日|catIdx=L劉}}），原名'''劉添爵'''<ref name="劉永身上有兩隻金鷄 片場裏人人叫仔陸小鷄">{{cite news | title=劉永身上有兩隻金鷄 片場裏人人叫仔陸小鷄 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgCcTQP34pXmE&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=22&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1977-05-29| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，是1970年代香港[[邵氏兄弟|邵氏兄弟]]男演員。其契爺是香港已故電影導演[[羅維_(導演)|羅維]]和[[李翰祥|李翰祥]]（已上契）{{noteTag|name=守下留情1|關於劉永加入嘉禾初期工作、跟李翰祥學習剪片和成為李翰祥上契契仔的資料出自香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2020年2月11日播出的訪問。}}<ref name="大地在我腳下劉永">{{cite web |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/blogger/shall-we-talk/20151031-6463 |title=大地在我腳下劉永 |last= |first= |date=2015-10-31 |website= |publisher=明周 |access-date=2020-02-11 |quote= |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202316/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/blogger/shall-we-talk/20151031-6463 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。劉曾出演1976年電影《乾隆皇帝奇遇記》中的「乾隆」以及1986年[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]的電視劇《[[秦始皇_(香港電視劇)|秦始皇]]》中「[[嬴政|嬴政]]」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/88685 |title=影城中的乾隆皇劉永 |last= |first= |date=2019-06-29|website= |publisher=東周刊 第826期 |access-date=2020-02-11 |quote= |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202300/https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/88685 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
===早年生活===
劉永的父親是海員{{noteTag|name=守下留情|關於劉永家庭背景、就讀學校、早年及校園生活、學習兼教授功夫和加入娛樂圈經過的資料出自香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2020年2月10日播出的訪問。}}，來到香港生活前是中國內地一所輪船公司的老闆兼地區首富，<ref name="保良局蔡繼有學校總校長劉筱玲：其實我想做小孩">{{cite web |url=http://cky.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/FAM2014april2.pdf |title=保良局蔡繼有學校總校長劉筱玲：其實我想做小孩 |last= |first= |date=2014-4 |website= |publisher=Fam101樂活.家 親子智慧資訊平台 |access-date=2020-02-11 |quote= |archive-date=2014-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604014531/http://cky.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/FAM2014april2.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。母親為劉永父親的中學同學兼香港著名[[甘草演員|甘草演員]][[黎雯|黎雯]]<ref name="劉永身上有兩隻金鷄 片場裏人人叫仔陸小鷄" /><ref name="保良局蔡繼有學校總校長劉筱玲：其實我想做小孩" />。他於[[香港|香港]]出生，有五姊一弟{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。其中二姊劉筱玲是[[保良局蔡繼有學校|保良局蔡繼有學校]]總校長<ref name="保良局蔡繼有學校總校長劉筱玲：其實我想做小孩" />。劉早年於[[九龍城|九龍城]][[聯合道|聯合道]][[香港華人基督教聯會九龍墳場|香港華人基督教聯會九龍墳場]]對面的侯王廟新村木屋區長大，時常到位於木屋區後面、白鶴山山腳聯合道6259號地段的[[國家片場|國家片場]]（現為賈炳達道公園）與[[七小福|七小福]]玩耍{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。又會到墳場領取吉儀作為零用錢之用{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。由於劉永母親不想兒子只顧嬉戲而無人管束，所以他在小學階段曾就讀三所學校{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。每天分別在[[福德學校|福德學校]]入讀上午校，下午到聖保祿詠思英文學校（小學部）上學，後到培正英文夜校（小學部）念書{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。升上[[鄧鏡波學校|鄧鏡波學校]]後，他無心向學，讀書成績較差{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。多花時間在參與校內籃球及足球活動方面{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。在學期間在校內教授[[日本|日本]]天一流正體術（柔術）{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。而自己會在外學習[[剛柔流|剛柔流]]三段{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。當認識[[李小龍|李小龍]]後更與[[林正英|林正英]]在李的舊居轉學自由搏擊功夫{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。劉永加入娛樂圈後曾與前藝人[[李道洪|李道洪]]一同到鄧鏡波學校教授自由搏擊{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。

===銀色旅途===
在十七歲，即1968年中學畢業後，劉跟其契爺[[羅維_(導演)|羅維]]拍攝電影，當他的副導演及場記<ref name="大地在我腳下劉永" />。也當過[[謝賢|謝賢]]的動作場面替身<ref name="大地在我腳下劉永" />。再於1970年留意到報紙廣告中有關[[嘉禾娛樂|嘉禾電影]]招收演員的啟示，於是向母親隱暪自己用自行創作的藝名「劉永」報考面試；結果母親准許他去嘗試於影圈發展{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。他便在1970年8月與[[苗可秀|苗可秀]]等合共三個女生與[[嘉禾|嘉禾]]簽下六年基本演員合約{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。劉永本身喜歡學武，學過[[六合八法拳|六合八法拳]]，參演過[[李小龍|李小龍]]《[[唐山大兄|唐山大兄]]》、《[[猛龍過江|猛龍過江]]》等作品。同期在黃家達的「香港忍者恒健練武館」擔任總教練<ref name="劉永開始被力捧 李小龍收他為徒">{{cite news | title=劉永開始被力捧 李小龍收他為徒 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2F3zFhASdgu4bKTpq84FWiV&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=58&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=5  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1972-11-19 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。劉與李小龍結緣於《唐山大兄》；他們其實識於微時{{noteTag|name=守下留情2|關於劉永認識李小龍和首部參與的電影的資料出自香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2020年2月12日播出的訪問。}}。李拍攝電影之際欣賞劉的功夫底子，所以向他教授[[截拳道|截拳道]]<ref name="劉永開始被力捧 李小龍收他為徒" />。而《唐山大兄》是劉永參演的首部電影作品{{noteTag|name=守下留情2}}。劉永後來於1975年在一次午夜場電影放映時認識[[方逸華|方逸華]]<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永專為陳萍解圍 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgJHkR1aakBHY&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=40&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=11  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1978-03-31| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，因而獲對方羅致到[[邵氏|邵氏]]<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永簽邵氏 可能改藝名 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58ICqkf4NaDXg6oDbxnCZYl&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=20&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1975-05-29| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，翌年在[[邵逸夫|邵逸夫]]欽點參演與李翰祥執導下<ref>{{cite news | title=李翰祥要拍乾隆皇 邵逸夫親口點劉永 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58W%2BpsjUUZMe9%2F6TRpNZu78&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=149&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1976-01-27| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，在《乾隆皇帝奇遇記》中扮演乾隆而大受歡迎，隨即主演多部乾隆皇帝系列電影。工餘時會跟李翰祥學習剪片技術{{noteTag|name=守下留情1}}。

劉永及後於1984年加入[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]，首部參演之劇集為《武則天》<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永初演電視劇 即獲觀眾來信讃 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFKJvpgmPEYLh&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=123&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1984-08-27| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。當年[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]邀請他加盟{{noteTag|name=守下留情3|關於劉永加入亞洲電視經過的資料出自香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2020年2月13日播出的訪問。}}。但[[邱德根|邱德根]]得知劉參與的電影在台灣禁播，遂親自找他加入亞洲電視{{noteTag|name=守下留情3}}。劉在1986年於重頭劇《[[秦始皇_(香港電視劇)|秦始皇]]》飾演男主角[[嬴政|嬴政]]而聲名大噪。他多數都是在亞視演出，甚少在[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]亮相。由於參演過中國大陸製作的電影，在台灣被定為「附匪藝人」，他所演出的劇集在1990年代初期曾被[[行政院新聞局|行政院新聞局]]禁播。嚴重傷害前妻[[戴良純|戴良純]]一事都使其參演之影片都受到台灣的禁制。另一方面，鑑於香港及台灣兩地沒有引渡條例，劉於上訴前潛逃返港<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永戲劇性返港會記者 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6Mn2EqtxLjcu1K&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=131&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=5  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1984-11-25 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，此後十年內沒有踏足當地受到法律制裁<ref>{{cite news | title=首任妻子戴良純被刀傷毀容 | url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20191018/00282_003.html | format= | publisher=東方日報 | date=2019-10-18 | accessdate=2020-02-11 | quote= | archive-date=2020-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202341/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20191018/00282_003.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。劉永入行以來得到兩次[[台灣|台灣]][[金馬獎|金馬獎]]提名。第一次是於1981年憑《[[大湖英烈|大湖英烈]]》獲得「最佳男主角」提名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=10&search_regist_year=1981&ins=16 |title=入圍得獎名單 |last= |first= |date=1981 |website= |publisher=台北金馬影展 |access-date=2020-02-11 |quote= |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202355/https://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=10&search_regist_year=1981&ins=16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；第二次是於2011年因電影《[[復仇者之死|復仇者之死]]》入圍[[金馬獎最佳男配角|金馬獎最佳男配角]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=10&search_regist_year=2011&ins=46 |title=入圍得獎名單 |last= |first= |date=2011 |website= |publisher=台北金馬影展 |access-date=2020-02-11 |quote= |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202403/https://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=10&search_regist_year=2011&ins=46 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年9月出席電影首映禮時表示將來會多返港工作，以賺錢供兒子升學<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永認自己無用 無錢供兒子讀書 | url=http://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/local/20170920-82057 | format= | publisher=明周 | date=2017-09-20| accessdate=2020-02-11 | quote= | archive-date=2017-09-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920142307/http://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/local/20170920-82057 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年成立其「劉永工作室」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.weibo.com/1566180822/ECakkhovn?type=comment#_rnd1581426220485 |title=大家午安---谢谢大家的支持---刘永工作室开业---开始努力奋斗啦…… |last= |first= |date=2017-03-30|website= |publisher=刘永-秦始皇微博 |access-date=2020-02-11|quote=}}</ref>，現時主要遊走於香港及中國大陸，在幕後任製片和參與幕前演出。

==惹上官非==
劉永在1977年因貪玩身藏[[彈弓刀|彈弓刀]]，遭警員查獲，<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永貪玩藏彈弓刀 遇上警探惹來官非 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58W%2BpsjUUZMe7yUJLjCEQPW&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=96&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1977-02-26| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>被[[九龍裁判署|九龍裁判署]]法官判處罰款二千港元<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永光頭‧法官好笑 藏刀一事‧罰欵二千 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58W%2BpsjUUZMeyTfWrkWZAOJ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=84&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1977-03-12| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。1979年再惹上官非，被指控與三名人士於[[清水灣|清水灣]]邵氏片場宿舍內恐嚇林姓男子簽署四張支票欠單<ref>{{cite news | title=涉嫌迫簽支票禁錮毆打 打仔明星劉永等押候審 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFETIbwGQtslu&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=115&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=2  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1987-09-01| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>，不過法庭撤銷控罪<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永吳元俊官司已撤銷 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2Bn4efK8nHqL%2B5KK3snjk8i&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=151&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1979-12-13 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。1983年又被控與徐姓男子在[[深水埗|深水埗]]毆傷蔡姓男子<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永涉嫌毆人 獲准保釋候審| url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58StS6UNkXpij3iBC%2BNFEam&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=194&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1983-12-31 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。

==個人生活==
劉永在電影界發展初期曾與[[恬妞|恬妞]]和[[文雪兒|文雪兒]]拍拖<ref>{{cite news | title=往事不願回味 恬妞避談劉永 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgJ4MSZ5nB%2BEB&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=24&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1978-01-14| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=劉永收回美孚樓 完全為母親健康 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgApA8ST5afmi&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=64&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=11  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1978-04-15| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。他為人熟悉的是他的兩段婚姻。第一任妻子為台灣藝人[[戴良純|戴良純]]，第二任妻子為首屆[[亞洲小姐|亞洲小姐]]冠軍[[黎燕珊|黎燕珊]]，兩人育有一子一女。兩段婚姻都是以離婚告終。有[[媒體|媒體]]指[[離婚|離婚]]原因是[[家暴|家暴]]，蓋因1984年劉永因用刀殺傷前妻[[戴良純|戴良純]]，並令她差點毀容而觸犯《[[中華民國刑法|中華民國刑法]]》，被以「殺人未遂罪」起訴且被[[台北地方法院|台北地方法院]]判處兩年半有期徒刑<ref>{{cite news | title=在台北被控傷妻未遂罪 劉永判監兩年半 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6Mn7umgZGlwmT0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1984-10-12 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。事件最後以賠償[[新台幣|新台幣]]600萬元和解<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永突然在港出現 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2Bh5KT9sfcXnHfZ729y0uHT&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=130&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=1  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1984-11-24 | accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。而第二任妻子黎燕珊於2000年更向香港法院申請禁制令，阻止劉永接觸一雙年幼的子女<ref>{{cite news | title=黎燕珊八年婚姻終了斷 | url=https://std.stheadline.com/archive/fullstory.asp?andor=or&year1=2001&month1=2&day1=17&year2=2001&month2=2&day2=17&category=all&id=20010217f08&keyword1=&keyword2= | format= | publisher=星島日報 | date=2001-02-17| accessdate=2020-02-11|quote= }}</ref>。2004年完成分居過程正式離婚。劉永其後在2007年娶了比他年輕三十歲的內地女子黃麗燕，兩人育有兩名兒子<ref>{{cite news | title=北上遇第三春老婆細30年 66歲劉永享受老夫少妻 | url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170925/20162903 | format= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2017-09-25| accessdate=2020-02-11 | quote= | archive-date=2019-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719170302/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170925/20162903 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終在2019年基於年齡差距出現代溝，引致離婚收場<ref>{{cite news | title=劉永遭內地嫩妻狠撇分身家 老年第三度離婚帶幼子回港生活 | url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2476658/%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AB%A9%E5%A6%BB%E7%8B%A0%E6%92%87%E5%88%86%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%B6%20%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%B8%B6%E5%B9%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB | format= | publisher=晴報 | date=2019-10-17 | accessdate=2020-02-11 | quote= | archive-date=2020-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124202537/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2476658/%E5%8A%89%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AB%A9%E5%A6%BB%E7%8B%A0%E6%92%87%E5%88%86%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%B6%20%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%B8%B6%E5%B9%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦由[[中山市|中山市]]搬回香港定居<ref name="68歲劉永與嫩口內地妻分居返港獨力養兩子" />。

1985年，劉永離開夜總會時被十名男子打至一條胸肋骨折斷，五條有裂痕。左眼眉骨暴裂，需要縫合九針，眼部微細血管受損，視線模糊不清<ref name="劉永挨揍真不單純 眾說紛紜滿城風雨">{{cite web |url=http://rtv789.blogspot.com/2017/12/12141986.html |title=劉永挨揍真不單純 眾說紛紜滿城風雨 |date=1986-01-12 |website= |publisher=TTV電視周刊1214期 |access-date=2021-07-27 |quote= |archive-date=2021-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727082432/http://rtv789.blogspot.com/2017/12/12141986.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。留醫一個月出院<ref name="劉永挨揍真不單純 眾說紛紜滿城風雨" />。

